quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,64,"O maaki: "Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wonaa no mi hoolornoo on non e musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni moЖґЖґo deenoowo, ko KaЕ‹ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude yurmotooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,65,"Nde Й“e ngudditunoo doЕ‹le maЙ“Й“e Й—een, Й“e tawi cogguuji(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ruttaama e maЙ“Й“e. ЖЃe mbi'i: "eeyma yo ben amen, ko men Й—aЙ“Й“ata [kadi]? ЖЉii ko cogguuji amen, Й—i nduttaama e amen. MiЙ—en njiggana yimЙ“e amen, men ndeena musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“eydora Й“etu ngelooba; Й—uum ko Й“etu newiingu"."
  12,66,"O maaki: "Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e mooЙ—on haa Жґettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonВґde on ngrtiranat kam mo si wonaa hara on kuЙ“inda". ЖЃaawo Й“e Жґettanii mo ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, o maaki: "Alla e dow ko wowluЙ—en kon, ko o deenoowo"."
  12,67,"O maaki: "eeheymin Й“iЙ—Й“e am, wota on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame ceertuЙ—e. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muyЙ—e) Alla hay e huunde. Г‘aawoore alanaa si wonaa Alla: Ko e makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,68,"Nde Й“e naatirnoo nokku ka baaba maЙ“Й“e yamirnoo Й“e Й—on, Й—um wonaano no duncana Й“e [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunooЙ—o e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. KaЕ‹ko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal min anndini mo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e nganndaa."
  12,69,"Nde Й“e naatnoo ka Yuusufa, o maЙ“Й“i musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: "Ko mi musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko Й“e ngollatnoo"."